•	Embedded Systems & Firmware Development – Gained expertise in C programming for PIC microcontrollers, integrating sensors, displays, and communication modules for real-time control.
•	Algorithm Design & Debugging – Strengthened skills in designing and refining control logic using flowcharts, debugging firmware in MPLAB X IDE, and ensuring system reliability.
•	Communication & Hardware Integration – Developed protocols for seamless data exchange between microcontrollers and external peripherals, improving system synchronization and efficiency
